OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports journalist Anna
OL,8,FYoussef spoke to 'Susie' about her
OL,9,Fordeal, and her wait for justice
OL,11,FA woman who was sexually assaulted by
OL,12,Fan "entitled, abusive and predatory"
OL,13,Fman posing as a taxi driver says she
OL,14,Fhopes speaking out will encourage
OL,15,Fothers to come forward - despite
OL,16,Fwaiting five years for justice.
OL,18,F'Susie' was just 17 when she was
OL,19,Fattacked by Tayumur Raja, 29, who had
OL,20,Fbeen driving around Oldham looking for
OL,21,Fvulnerable victims.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,FHe approached the teenager, who had
OL,8,Fjust left a nightclub in the town and
OL,9,Fwas waiting for a taxi home, and -
OL,10,Fbelieving it to be her ride - she got
OL,11,Finto the car.
OL,13,F"He was literally looking for someone
OL,14,F- you can see that on the CCTV because
OL,15,Fthere was no other reason for him to
OL,16,Fbe there," Susie, whose identity is
OL,17,Fbeing protected, said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,F"I just looked vulnerable, I was on my
OL,8,Fown, I was only small and I was just
OL,9,Fin the wrong place at the wrong time.
OL,10,FI was just on my own and there was no
OL,11,Fone else around."
OL,13,FDuring the assault, at 4.15am on 25
OL,14,FSeptember 2021, she managed to fight
OL,15,Foff her attacker and get out of the
OL,16,Fcar, alerting a local shop for help.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,FBut, despite reporting it immediately
OL,8,Fto police, with Raja arrested and
OL,9,Fcharged soon after, Susie has had to
OL,10,Fwait five years to see her attacker
OL,11,Fbrought to justice and sentenced for
OL,12,Fher ordeal.
OL,14,FAt Bolton Crown Court, on 22 April
OL,15,F2026, Raja - who has been on bail
OL,16,Fsince his arrest - was jailed for nine
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,FJailing him Judge Abigail Hudson said
OL,8,Fhis attitude towards women was
OL,9,Fentitled, abusive and predatory,
OL,10,Fadding he posed a particular risk to
OL,11,Fstrangers.
OL,13,FShe also apologised to Susie for the
OL,14,Fsignificant distress caused by the
OL,15,Fdelay in this case coming to court and
OL,16,Fsaid she could not offer any
OL,17,Fexplanation or excuse, other than
OL,18,Ffunding.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,FDespite the delay, the teenager says
OL,8,Fshe is determined to show people
OL,9,Fattackers can, and will, be brought to
OL,10,Fjustice.
OL,12,F"I hope he never gets the chance to
OL,13,Fmake anyone feel like the way he made
OL,14,Fme feel," Susie said.
OL,16,F"I just wanted to make sure people
OL,17,Fknew you can get through it, you can
OL,18,Fgo to court and justice does happen
OL,19,Fsometimes."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,FRecounting the night of her attack
OL,8,FSusie said she believed that he would
OL,9,Ftake her home following a night out
OL,10,Fwith friends.
OL,12,F"I just got in the back of the car as
OL,13,Fyou do in a taxi, and then he just
OL,14,Fstarted off driving so I thought,
OL,15,F'right I'm going home now' and then he
OL,16,Fdrove the total wrong way," she said.
OL,18,F"I knew something was going to happen,
OL,19,FI just didn't know what was going to
OL,20,Fhappen."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,FThey drove to an empty carpark, where
OL,8,FRaja began doing drugs, promising he
OL,9,Fwould take her home when he had
OL,10,Ffinished.
OL,12,F"I just kept on saying I want to go
OL,13,Fhome just take me home and he was like
OL,14,F- let me do just a quick line," she
OL,15,Fadded.
OL,17,FWith her phone dead and the doors
OL,18,Flocked, Susie was trapped inside the
OL,19,Fcar, and she was dragged into the
OL,20,Ffront passenger seat where she was
OL,21,Fsexually assaulted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,F"I was just telling him to stop. I
OL,8,Ftold him, 'I just want to go home, I
OL,9,Fjust want to go home, stop stop', I
OL,10,Fwas crying," she said.
OL,12,F"While I was trying to get out he was
OL,13,Ftrying to pull me back in by my neck
OL,14,Fbecause that's all he could grab hold
OL,15,Fof.
OL,17,F"He gets back into the driver's seat,
OL,18,Fstarts the car and starts driving
OL,19,Fafter me so I thought he's going to
OL,20,Fhit me with a car here."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,FResearch by the charity Rape Crisis
OL,8,Fhas found the number of sexual offence
OL,9,Fcases waiting to go to court is at a
OL,10,Frecord high - with 14,749 on the
OL,11,Fwaiting list.
OL,13,FThe number represents a 75% increase
OL,14,Fin the past three years, with the
OL,15,Fbacklog meaning one in three rape
OL,16,Ftrials ends up being postponed at
OL,17,Fleast once.
OL,19,FAlison Lloyd from Greater Manchester
OL,20,FRape Crisis says survivors lives are
OL,21,Fbeing put on hold
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,F"The impact on the survivors is very
OL,8,Freal and often devastating," Alison
OL,9,FLloyd from Greater Manchester Rape
OL,10,FCrisis said.
OL,12,F"Any survivor of sexual harm deserves
OL,13,Fa process that supports recovery and
OL,14,Fnot one that promotes trauma.
OL,16,F"We hear from survivors who feel as
OL,17,Fthought their lives are on hold for
OL,18,Fyears, unable to move on, constantly
OL,19,Fanxious and living with repeated
OL,20,Funcertainty about their cases and when
OL,21,Fthey will be heard."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,FSpeaking of the five-year delay, Susie
OL,8,Fadded: "It just made it harder because
OL,9,Fyou had to remember every little
OL,10,Fdetail, every little thing.
OL,12,F"You can't ever put it behind you,
OL,13,Fbecause you are constantly thinking
OL,14,F'well I have got court so it has got
OL,15,Fto be brought back up' so if you push
OL,16,Fit too far down it has got to be
OL,17,Fbrought back up again so you are
OL,18,Fconstantly thinking about it until it
OL,19,Fis done."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police said Raja
OL,8,Fshowed no remorse for his actions
OL,9,Fthroughout the investigation and
OL,10,Fcontinually denied the offence.
OL,12,FAt one point during his interview, he
OL,13,Flaughed when it was explained to him
OL,14,Fthat the allegation was a serious one
OL,15,Fand that there was a need to ask him
OL,16,Fquestions about it. He declined to
OL,17,Fcomment and claimed the victim had
OL,18,Fgiven consent.
OL,20,FBut on 6 March 2026 Raja was convicted
OL,21,Fof sexual assault.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,FDetective Constable Paul Fay, Oldham
OL,8,FCID, said: "I commend the bravery of
OL,9,Fthe victim-survivor. Thanks to her, a
OL,10,Fdangerous sexual predator is now
OL,11,Fbehind bars.
OL,13,F"I hope this gives the victim a sense
OL,14,Fof justice as she looks to move
OL,15,Fforward and rebuild her life.
OL,26,@pD@LOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,F"I urge all victim-survivors of rape
OL,8,Fand sexual offences to please come
OL,9,Fforward and report them to us. You
OL,10,Fwill be believed and supported. We can
OL,11,Fwork at a pace that suits you so we
OL,12,Fcan bring perpetrators to justice."
OL,14,FA spokesperson for the Ministry of
OL,15,FJustice said it was investing
OL,16,F#500million in victim support and a
OL,17,Fnew national legal advice service for
OL,18,Fvictims of rape.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1776888354
OL,3,CBogus taxi driver jailed for
OL,4,Cassaulting teen after five year wait
OL,5,Cfor justice
OL,7,FIt added: "The Crown Court is under
OL,8,Fsevere pressure, with more than 80,000
OL,9,Foutstanding cases and victims facing
OL,10,Funacceptable delays after years of
OL,11,Fneglect.
OL,13,F"Through reform, record investment and
OL,14,Fmodernisation, we are working to cut
OL,15,Fthe backlog and deliver swift, fair
OL,16,Fjustice.''
OL,26,@oD@KOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/16
